videos.headline: Buckeyes gets dream start with pick-six
videos.description: On the opening drive of the game, Tommy Armstrong Jr.'s pass gets tipped into the air and into the hands of Damon Webb who goes the rest of the way for the Ohio State defensive touchdown.

videos.headline: Nebraska Receivers are in sync on the tip drill
videos.description: Tommy Armstrong Jr. pass complete to Stanley Morgan Jr. for 26 yds to the OhSt 30 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Buckeyes strike again with TD pass to McLaurin
videos.description: J.T. Barrett avoids the pressure and then finds Terry McLaurin from seven yards out to increase Ohio State's lead to 14-3 over Nebraska.

videos.headline: Buckeyes cash in again with 23-yard Mike Weber TD
videos.description: Ohio State starts putting daylight between themselves and Nebraska when Mike Weber sweeps left and goes 23 yards into the end zone to put the Buckeyes up 21-3.

videos.headline: Nebraska recovers fumble on punt
videos.description: Caleb Lightbourn punt for 39 yds , Dontre Wilson returns for no gain to the OhSt 38 Dontre Wilson fumbled, recovered by Neb Luke McNitt

videos.headline: Scary scene as Tommy Armstrong Jr. goes down injured
videos.description: While scrambling for yards, Tommy Armstrong Jr. gets hit and lands on his head before lying motionless on the ground. He showed signs of movement later and was taken off to the hospital on a stretcher and to the hospital.

videos.headline: Nebraska training staff tends to QB Armstrong
videos.description: Nebraska training staff tends to QB Tommy Armstrong Jr. with his dad and girlfriend at his side.

videos.headline: Armstrong gives a thumbs up as he's carted off
videos.description: Nebraska QB Tommy Armstrong Jr. gives the crowd a thumbs up as he is carted off and into an ambulance.

videos.headline: J.T. Barrett rushes for 20 yards to convert on 3rd down
videos.description: J.T. Barrett run for 20 yds to the OhSt 36 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Buckeyes strike again just before halftime
videos.description: Ohio State caps off a 15-play, 85-yard drive when J.T. Barrett hits Curtis Samuel on the jump pass to increase Ohio State's lead heading into halftime to 31-3.

videos.headline: Buckeyes open second half with 75-yard TD
videos.description: On the first snap of the second half, J.T. Barrett airs it out to Curtis Samuel who makes the catch and gets through the tackle to find the end zone and boost Ohio State's lead to 38-3.

videos.headline: J. Barrett pass to N. Brown for 6 yds for a TD
videos.description: J.T. Barrett pass complete to Noah Brown for 6 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Armstrong carted off the field after diving headfirst
videos.description: Nebraska QB Tommy Armstrong runs to the Ohio State sideline but doesn't have time to brace for impact and dives headfirst to the ground. Medical staff rush to Armstrong's aid as he lies unconscious and eventually leaves the stadium in an ambulance.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Armstrong carted off the field after diving headfirst) 2016/11/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ohio State's second pick-six continues the rout
videos.description: Ohio State just keeps on scoring, even while on defense as Malik Hooker makes it two pick-sixes on the night for the Buckeyes to go up 55-3.

videos.headline: Ohio State continues dominance against Nebraska
videos.description: Joe Burrow run for 12 yds for a TD

videos.headline: No. 6 Ohio State wins big over No. 10 Nebraska
videos.description: Curtis Samuel rushes for 178 yards and two touchdowns in Ohio State's 62-3 win over Nebraska while the Cornhuskers lost QB Tommy Armstrong to a scary head injury in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Meyer, Riley stunned by Buckeyes' dominance
videos.description: Ohio State coach Urban Meyer and Nebraska coach Mike Riley both admit they didn't see the Buckeyes dominating the way they did.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Presser (Meyer, Riley stunned by Buckeyes' dominance) 2016/11/05 ESHEET
